it is a process where we use mongodb helm chart
mongo-express with the classic way
ingress, using a helm chart


# helm-mongodb.yaml
# after adding the bitnami Helm repo
## helm repo add bitnami https://charts.bitnami.com/bitnami
# helm install mongodb --values helm-mongodb.yaml bitnami/mongodb

# helm-ingress.yaml
# after adding the the ingress-nginx Helm repo
## helm repo add ingress-nginx https://kubernetes.github.io/ingress-nginx
# helm install ingress-nginx ingress-nginx/ingress-nginx --set controller.publishService.enabled=true
